<h3>Viewing Photos</h3><p>To view photos, select an album below. Once you have selected a photo you can scroll through using the left and right arrow keys.</p><h3>Purchasing Photos</h3><p>To purchase a photo use the "Add to Basket" option shown next to a photo once you have selected it.</p><p>To view your shopping basked click the "Shopping Basket" option in the top right corner.</p>